Meyer Burger Acquires 6.3% of Roth & Rau to Raise Shareholding to 17.7%

-- B y   P a u l   V e r s c h u u r
-- 
2011-04-21T04:37:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/meyer-burger-acquires-6-3-of-roth-rau-to-raise-shareholding-to-17-7-.html
Meyer Burger Technology AG (MBTN)  said it
bought a further 6.3 percent of  Roth & Rau AG (R8R)  at 22 euros per
share from OTB Group BV of the Netherlands, taking its stake in
the German company to 17.7 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Verschuur at 
 pverschuur@bloomberg.net  